         <div type="metricalScheme">
            <p>Madrigale con doppio ritornello 10’a 10’b 10’b, 10’c 10’d 10’d; 10’e 10’e; 10’f 10’f.</p>
            <p><hi rend="italic">Capovilla </hi>XLIX.</p>
            <p>Punti sottoscritti: v. 1 (<hi rend="italic">titolo</hi>) Lu; v. 2 (<hi rend="italic">festi</hi>) Lu; v. 6 (<hi rend="italic">sposo</hi>) Lu; v. 7 (<hi rend="italic">questo</hi>) Lu; v. 8 (<hi rend="italic">novo</hi>), (<hi rend="italic">triumfi</hi>) Lu.</p>
         </div>


